  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Salsa Fresca</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Salsa Fresca</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetable\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetable\">Vegetable</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>. It is cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Toma_Root\" title=\"Toma Root\">Toma Root</a>, an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Onion\" title=\"Onion\">Onion</a> and two fillers. Fillers cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedibles\" title=\"Inedibles\">Inedibles</a>, or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a>. Salsa Fresca takes 10 seconds to cook.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Toma_Roots\" title=\"Toma Roots\"><img alt=\"Toma Roots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Toma_Roots.png?4ccad5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Onions\" title=\"Onions\"><img alt=\"Onions.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Onions.png?f753db\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Salsa_Fresca\" title=\"Salsa Fresca\"><img alt=\"Salsa Fresca.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Salsa_Fresca.png?e960e6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Fillers cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedibles\" title=\"Inedibles\">Inedibles</a>, or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Toma_Roots\" title=\"Toma Roots\"><img alt=\"Toma Roots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Toma_Roots.png?4ccad5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Onions\" title=\"Onions\"><img alt=\"Onions.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Onions.png?f753db\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a