4\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Salsa_Fresca\" title=\"Salsa Fresca\"><img alt=\"Salsa Fresca.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Salsa_Fresca.png?e960e6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Salsa Fresca was added to <i>Don&#x27;t Starve Together</i> in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a>&#x27;s <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together/Version_History#July_25,_2019_-_Warly_Character_Update\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together/Version History\">Character Update</a>.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Salsa_Fresca#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Salsa_Fresca#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
