  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nSalsa Fresca\nFood Info\n25\n3\n33\nVeggie\nObject Info\n15 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x2\n10 sec\n20\nMiscellaneous\n\"salsa\"\n“So... hot...!”\n–Wilson\n“Hey, this is great!”\n–Willow\n“Is a tasty sauce!”\n–Wolfgang\n“I don't feel much like dancing.”\n–Wendy\n“PRE CRUSHED FOR EASY CONSUMPTION”\n–WX-78\n“My goodness, that has some zest to it!”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Lucy'll give ya a hand chopping veggies next time, eh bud?”\n–Woodie\n“A bit spicy for my delicate palate.”\n–Maxwell\n“A disappointing mush.”\n–Wigfrid\n“Yummy but... spicy!!”\n–Webber\n“I like to spice things up!”\n–Warly\n“Tasty mush”\n–Wormwood\n“Wish I had some chips to go with this.”\n–Winona\n“A spicy treat for mortals to eat.”\n–Wortox\n“Spicy veggie mush!”\n–Wurt\n“It only comes with one chip?!”\n–Walter\n“I guess I could spare some time for a quick snack...”\n–Wanda\nSalsa Fresca is a Vegetable Food Item exclusive to Don't Starve Together. It is cooked in the Crock Pot by combining a Toma Root, an Onion and two fillers. Fillers cannot be Meats, Inedibles, or Eggs. Salsa Fresca takes 10 seconds to cook.\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×2\nFillers cannot be Meats, Inedibles, or Eggs.\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×2\n×2\n×2\n×2\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nSalsa Fresca was added to Don't Starve Together in Warly's Character Update.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
